   "html": "1877 － 1954"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ まつもと・じょうじ ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n商工相、憲法問題調査会会長、東大教授、商法学者、内閣法制局長官、貴族院議員、満鉄副社長"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"07m.html\">一覧　（マ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E6%259D%25BE%25E6%259C%25AC%2520%25E7%2583%259D%25E6%25B2%25BB\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　東京都出身。東京帝大卒業後、ドイツ、フランス、イギリスに留学し、法学を学ぶ。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　母校の教授となり、商法、民法の講座を担当。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　大学退職後、南満州鉄道株式会社の理事、ついで副社長。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1923/yamm2_1.html\">山本内閣②</a>の法制局長官、<a href=\"../1932/saito_1.html\">斉藤内閣</a>の商工相などを歴任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　手形法、小切手法、有限会社法の制定、商法改正などに指導的役割を果たす。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、<a href=\"../1945/side_1.html\">幣原内閣</a>の国務相となり、憲法問題調査会会長に就任。いわゆる<a href=\"../1946/02matum.html\">「松本案」を作成</a>。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「ＧＨＱ案」に消極的抵抗を試みるも、受け入れられなかった。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
